'''Umugezi wa Sebeya''' ni uruzi ruri mu [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|Ntara y'Iburengerazuba]], u [[Rwanda]] rusohoka mu [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|kiyaga cya Kivu]] giherereye mu majyepfo y'umujyi wa Gisenyi. Umugezi wa Sebeya ukomoka mu misozi y'[[akarere ka Rutsiro]].Ipima kilometero 110 z'uburebure bwamazi irimo kilometero kare 286  y'[[Akarere ka Rutsiro|aturere ka Rutsiro]], [[Akarere ka Ngororero|Ngororero]] na [[Akarere ka Rubavu|Rubavu]].<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sebeya_River</ref>

